<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:09:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特拉维夫郊区发生刺伤袭击，两名以色列人死亡，两人受伤；攻击者射击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-live/idf-about-30-rockets-fired-in-barrage-on-north-combat-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-gaza/00000191-1b5b-dd06-a3f7-9b5f2cc50000</link><description>一名男子受伤死亡，刺伤事件中的死亡人数增加至两人；两人仍在住院 ■ 美联社报道，以色列国防军在加沙的空袭造成 12 人死亡，其中四人死在收容流离失所者的帐篷营地内 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹落在以色列北部的拜特希勒尔 ■ 据半岛电视台报道，空军袭击加沙中部医院造成三人死亡■ 加拿大警告公民“避免前往以色列” ■ 约旦呼吁公民尽快离开黎巴嫩</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 03:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-live/idf-about-30-rockets-fired-in-barrage-on-north-combat-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-gaza/00000191-1b5b-dd06-a3f7-9b5f2cc50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备反击伊朗，内塔尼亚胡却让公众蒙在鼓里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-for-irans-counterattack-netanyahu-leaves-the-public-in-the-dark/00000191-19ae-db97-a7df-fdfee73e0000</link><description>与四月份不同的是，德黑兰对以色列遭受的袭击保持无线电沉默。与此同时，政府已免于向公民解释会发生什么，而总理正忙于推翻以色列国防部长的运动</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 03:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-for-irans-counterattack-netanyahu-leaves-the-public-in-the-dark/00000191-19ae-db97-a7df-fdfee73e0000</guid></item><item><title>美国官员：拜登意识到内塔尼亚胡在人质交易上向他撒谎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-biden-realized-netanyahu-lied-to-him-about-hostage-deal/00000191-19c0-d051-a3f7-d9cc68ce0000</link><description>拜登政府一名高级官员告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡对美国“忘恩负义”，并指出总理和拜登之间的过去两次对话既艰难又紧张</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 20:32:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-biden-realized-netanyahu-lied-to-him-about-hostage-deal/00000191-19c0-d051-a3f7-d9cc68ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列全国各地抗议，人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</link><description>人质亲属发誓不会放弃要求达成人质协议的示威活动，而通常每周举行的反政府抗议活动因担心伊朗或其代理人发动袭击而被取消</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:42:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第302天：人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</link><description>以色列谈判小组高级成员告诉《国土报》，以色列国防部长认为总理内塔尼亚胡对释放人质/停火协议不感兴趣 ■ 据报道，瑞典关闭了驻贝鲁特的贝鲁特大使馆，美国、英国敦促黎巴嫩国民尽快离开该国■ 以色列摩萨德和辛贝特领导人前往埃及并返回以色列继续停战谈判 ■ 战争开始 302 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于地区紧张局势和价格飙升，这些航空公司削减了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</link><description>到目前为止，所有为以色列服务的美国航空公司以及几家欧洲航空公司都已暂停航班。以色列旗舰航空公司以色列航空维持正常航班，但票价却飙升</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>官员警告称，恐怖组织利用阿拉伯犯罪组织袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</link><description>以色列国防官员警告部长们，“有组织犯罪对国家安全构成战略威胁”，并警告外国恐怖组织已经试图利用以色列境内的犯罪组织实施袭击。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 15:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人阿尔乔姆·多尔戈皮亚特在巴黎奥运会体操自由体操决赛中获得银牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</link><description>多尔戈皮亚特的胜利使以色列的奥运奖牌总数达到 19 枚，其中 6 枚是在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上获得的</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列人质埃坦·利维 (Eitan Levy) 的家人公布了加沙人踢打、虐待他身体的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</link><description>利维于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被运往加沙。视频显示，利维的尸体在一辆汽车的敞开的后备箱中，后来躺在地上，而加沙人则对其进行拳打脚踢。 Levy是一名53岁的出租车司机，10月7日在载着一名乘客前往加沙边境时被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》摄影师拍摄的以色列一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures/00000191-1865-dd1b-a9f5-ff6d46a00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 13:56:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures/00000191-1865-dd1b-a9f5-ff6d46a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸图尔卡尔姆；巴勒斯坦人报告九人死亡，其中包括哈马斯指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/israeli-army-strikes-west-bank-palestinians-report-nine-dead-including-hamas-commander/00000191-17a4-df57-afd7-f7b633bd0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们使用无人机在图尔卡尔姆击落了一辆载有恐怖分子的车辆，并声称车内人员正在前往发动袭击的路上。军队第二次袭击图尔卡姆，目击者称两次袭击造成九人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 13:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/israeli-army-strikes-west-bank-palestinians-report-nine-dead-including-hamas-commander/00000191-17a4-df57-afd7-f7b633bd0000</guid></item><item><title>汤姆·鲁文尼 (Tom Reuveni) 夺得金牌，莎朗·坎特 (Sharon Kantor) 夺得银牌；以色列奖牌数增至五枚，创本届奥运会历史最高奖牌数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sharon-kantor-wins-olympic-silver-tom-reuveni-guarantees-medal-at-semi-finals/00000191-181a-d68e-a79b-5b9fdb110000</link><description>21 岁的坎特 (Kantor) 在女子组比赛中获得银牌后不久，23 岁的鲁文尼 (Reuveni) 在 IQFoil 组别中赢得了金牌。这些奖牌使以色列的奥运奖牌总数达到 18 枚，其中 5 枚是在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上获得的</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 12:10:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sharon-kantor-wins-olympic-silver-tom-reuveni-guarantees-medal-at-semi-finals/00000191-181a-d68e-a79b-5b9fdb110000</guid></item><item><title>报告：哈尼亚遇刺后希腊“高度戒备”针对以色列目标的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</link><description>据希腊《Kathimerini》报纸报道，希腊当局正在与外国情报机构联系，了解有关雅典以色列或犹太人目标遭受袭击的威胁加剧的报道。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 10:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列摩萨德雇佣伊朗特工在哈马斯头目哈尼亚的房间里放置炸药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</link><description>伊朗消息人士告诉《每日电讯报》，负责高级官员安全的革命卫队特工在哈马斯领导人被杀的德黑兰宾馆的另外两个房间里安放了爆炸装置</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 07:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</guid></item><item><title>英国和美国鼓励公民尽快离开黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-live/haniyeh-killing-carried-out-by-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-u-s-moves-warships-to-mideast/00000191-155d-dba6-a59d-175f1a530000</link><description>伊朗：将在“适当的时间、地点和方式”对哈马斯头目被杀进行“严厉”的报复 ■ 报告：17 岁儿童在黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生 ■ 据哈马斯媒体报道，以色列的袭击导致加沙学校 15 人死亡办公室 ■ 以色列定居者焚烧约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦农田 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，约旦河西岸图尔卡姆的袭击造成 9 人死亡 ■ 美国国防部长命令海军巡洋舰和驱逐舰前往中东</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 01:35:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-live/haniyeh-killing-carried-out-by-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-u-s-moves-warships-to-mideast/00000191-155d-dba6-a59d-175f1a530000</guid></item><item><title>战争会迎来以色列的救赎吗？弥赛亚狂热不仅受到宗教狂热分子的欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/war-will-usher-in-israels-redemption-messianic-fervor-gains-popularity-beyond-fanatics/00000191-14c4-df57-afd7-f6f6e4bb0000</link><description>灾难是世界末日预言传播者的沃土</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 23:55:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/war-will-usher-in-israels-redemption-messianic-fervor-gains-popularity-beyond-fanatics/00000191-14c4-df57-afd7-f6f6e4bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击了两个巴勒斯坦村庄，一小时内杀死了两人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-raided-two-palestinian-villages-and-killed-two-men-within-an-hour/00000191-14f7-d4cf-afb5-5cf715340000</link><description>士兵们杀害了一名巴勒斯坦社会工作者，这名社会工作者恳求他们让一辆载着一名临产妇女的救护车通过。他们向死者家发射催泪瓦斯，还杀死了另一名投掷石块的男子</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 22:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-raided-two-palestinian-villages-and-killed-two-men-within-an-hour/00000191-14f7-d4cf-afb5-5cf715340000</guid></item><item><title>越来越多的耶路撒冷保安人员是巴勒斯坦人。这就是为什么这是一个充满希望的发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/many-jerusalem-security-guards-are-palestinian-heres-why-thats-a-hopeful-development/00000191-143b-d116-a9db-dc7f45130000</link><description>商场和停车场的巴勒斯坦保安只是一个巨大现象的冰山一角：耶路撒冷的巴勒斯坦居民融入以色列当地社会</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/many-jerusalem-security-guards-are-palestinian-heres-why-thats-a-hopeful-development/00000191-143b-d116-a9db-dc7f45130000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，以色列国防部长认为内塔尼亚胡对加沙协议不感兴趣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/israeli-defense-chiefs-believe-netanyahu-isnt-interested-in-gaza-deal-top-official-says/00000191-14a0-d4cf-afb5-5cf5a8aa0000</link><description>以色列谈判团队的高级成员描述了内塔尼亚胡和高级国防官员之间在人质交易上的“分歧”；电视报道援引了总理